{"type":"answer","id":45220,"parentType":"question","parentId":7333,"uid":12320,"contents":"亮明立场：本人自干五，非五毛。拥护中国共产党，拥护习近平主席。本人努力学习习近平新时代中国特色社会主席思想，号召全体中国人民团结在以习近平同志为核心的党中央周围，实现中华民族的伟大复兴！<br>\n<br>\n==============================<br>\n<br>\n无论是统计数据还是观感，台湾经济在过去三十年来稳步增长，即使在1998年和2008年周边国家经济危机的环境下，也没有发生严重的衰退。<br>\n工资随经济发展也稳步增长。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://image3.thenewslens.com/2018/12/sidq9fng7kpfr57k17wx15nxefjtnh.jpeg?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://image3.thenewslens.com/2018/12/sidq9fng7kpfr57k17wx15nxefjtnh.jpeg?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" alt=\"https://image3.thenewslens.com/2018/12/sidq9fng7kpfr57k17wx15nxefjtnh.jpeg?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.ceicdata.com/datapage/charts/ipc_taiwan_forecast-gdp-ppp-per-capita?type=area&amp;period=max&amp;lang=en\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.ceicdata.com/datapage/charts/ipc_taiwan_forecast-gdp-ppp-per-capita?type=area&amp;period=max&amp;lang=en\" alt=\"https://www.ceicdata.com/datapage/charts/ipc_taiwan_forecast-gdp-ppp-per-capita?type=area&amp;period=max&amp;lang=en\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-08-30","agreeCount":-2,"discussionCount":1}